# React Rules

Use

React

TypeScript

Functional Components

Hooks

Never use class components.

Business logic belongs outside React.

Components should

Render UI

Handle user interaction

Call services

Nothing more.

Prefer

Composition

Small components

Reusable components

Avoid prop drilling.

Use Zustand.

Accessibility is required.

Every interactive element

must have

keyboard support

focus styles

ARIA labels

Prefer optimistic UI.

Loading states should use skeletons.

Avoid spinner-only interfaces.
